<section class="marketing green">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="one column">&nbsp;</div>
      <div class="six columns">
        <h2>Free, Anonymous and Open-Source</h2>
        <p>
          You can use Veeta however you want, for free, forever. You don't have to sign in with Facebook or give us your email. You can look at our source code and run a copy of it yourself.
